data.description: Beautiful, well kept home with game room and Solar panels. Home sits on a large lot with no house to the rear. Solar panels will be paid off at closing by seller. Providing FREE energy for the life of the home. Entryway leads to a large/open family room that has a ton of natural light. 1st floor has vinyl plank throughout. Spacious laundry room located near all the BR's upstairs. Perfect home for every type of home buyer; located in a quite cul-de-sac, walking distance to neighborhood pool/playground, walk/biking/jogging trail. Currently, leased till January 31, 2024. Call agent for more information.
